1. *Dar* je najveći dar koji možeš pokloniti nekome. (Gift is the greatest gift you can give someone.)
2. Oni su nam dali *dar* da uživamo u lepoti. (They gave us the gift to enjoy beauty.)
3. Njegove oči su bile *dar* od neba. (His eyes were a gift from heaven.)
4. Njegov *dar* za muziku je bio neprocenjiv. (His gift for music was priceless.)
5. Ona je hrabra i inteligentna - pravi *dar* s kojim se rađa. (She is brave and intelligent - a true gift with which one is born.)